<CENTER>
<h1>A Citizens' Guide<br>

to the State Budget Mess</h1>

<I><B>A Menu of 217 Proposals</B></I>
<P>
<I><B>to Reduce State Government Spending </B></I>
<P>
</center>

<pre>

