<P>
Comments: Certification and regulatory functions should be performed
by private professional associations and institutions of learning.
 In addition to the savings noted below, the public would save
$955,000 in annual permitting fees
<P>
Savings: $1.659 million (GF)
<P>
<B>1110.  Abolish regulatory functions of Medical Board of California
