http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/claremont/gsp/gsp30.htm 204.71.237.92 19970114115951 text/html 34404
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 12:00:09 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 08:11:46 GMT
