<P>
   Other 7.9%  (39)
<P>
2. Which of the following grade levels are offered at your school?
 
<P>
 (Check all which apply)
<P>
  Kindergarten 81.0% (419)
<P>
  1st Grade 80.0% (413)
<P>
  2nd Grade 80.0% (412)
<P>
  3rd Grade 79.0% (410)
<P>
  4th Grade 77.0% (401)
<P>
  5th Grade 77.0% (400)
