<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST96/Hooters.ST1996.html 204.71.237.92 19970114123753 text/html 7251
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 12:38:04 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 15-Jul-96 13:59:23 GMT
Content-length: 7067
