<DOCHDR>
http://www.mediaresearch.org:80/free/ST96/Airlie.ST1996.html 204.71.237.92 19970114123825 text/html 7494
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 12:38:39 GMT
