<hr  WIDTH=50%>
<p>
<h2><i>National Review</i></h2>
<hr WIDTH=30%>
<br>Below is a small sampling of the contents of the July 1, 1996 issue of National Review.
<br>
<br> 
<ul>
<li><a HREF="/nationalreview/01july96/week.html">The Week</a>
</li>
<br> <li><a HREF="/nationalreview/01july96/feature.html">Is The War On Drugs <I>Really</I> Lost: 400 Readers Give Their Views</a>
</li>
<br> 
<li><a HREF="/nationalreview/01july96/rusty.html">Dear Rusty</a></li>
<br>
<li><a HREF="/nationalreview/01july96/buckley.html">Higinbotham-D'Amato-Hillary</a>
by William F. Buckley, Jr. </li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>
</DOC>
