<html>
<head>
<BODY bgcolor=#ffffff>
<title>National Review --170696</title>
</head>
<body>
<center>
<img src="/nationalreview/arts.gif" border=0  height=100 width =425>
<br>
<hr  WIDTH=50%>
<p>
<h2><i>National Review</i></h2>
<hr WIDTH=30%>
<br>Below is a small sampling of the contents of the June 17, 1996 issue of National Review.
<br>
<br> 
<ul>
<li><a HREF="/nationalreview/17june96/week.html">The Week</a>
</li>
<br> <li><a HREF="/nationalreview/17june96/feature.html">Rude Awakening</a>
</li>
<br> 
